ue\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jnk1665702665688.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jnk1665702665688.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jnk1665702665688.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jnk1665702665688\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $formfocus\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"jnk1665702665688___formfocus_266931\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the name of the Form instance that has focus.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jnk1665702665688__topic_d83924e1_d83925e1_d83926e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jnk1665702665688__p_d83927e1_d83928e1_d83929e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formfocus</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jnk1665702665688__topic_d55522e1_d55523e1_d55524e1_d55525e1_d55526e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d194693e66\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jnk1665702665688__p_d83933e1_d83934e1_d83935e1\">String that contains the name of the form instance (or form in a sequence of modal forms) that currently has focus.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jnk1665702665688__topic_d55527e1_d55528e1_d55529e1_d55530e1_d55531e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d194693e75\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jnk1665702665688__d5909e20\">Use in Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jnk1665702665688__topic_d55532e1_d55533e1_d55534e1_d55535e1_d55536e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d194693e84\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jnk1665702665688__p_d83945e1_d83946e1_d83947e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formfocus</span> function is particularly useful in (local) services and global ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jnk1665702665688__section_qhb_xsz_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d194693e97\">Example: Reporting the Instance that has Focus </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example reports the name of the instance that currently\n               has focus in the message frame:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jnk1665702665688__pre_xwn_xsz_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">putmess \"The form instance %%$formfocus has focus.\"\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tod1665702665614.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>setformfocus</a><p>Set the focus to the specified component instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jzq1665702665465.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger getFocus (Form)</a><p>Interactive trigger that responds to the form getting focus.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oxi1665702665543.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger loseFocus (Form)</a><p>ProcScript module that responds to the form losing focus. It can be used to verify the data to ensure that it is complete or correct.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528960\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528960\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$formfocus Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $formfocus Return the name of the Form instance that has focus. $formfocus Return Values String that contains the name of the form instance (or form in a sequence of modal forms) that currently has focus. Use Use in Form components. Description The $formfocus function is particularly useful in (local) services and global ProcScript. Example: Reporting the Instance that has Focus The following example reports the name of the instance that currently has focus in the message frame: putmess \"The form instance %%$formfocus has focus.\" Copy Related Links setformfocus Set the focus to the specified component instance. trigger getFocus (Form) Interactive trigger that responds to the form getting focus. trigger loseFocus (Form) ProcScript module that responds to the form losing focus. It can be used to verify the data to ensure that it is complete or correct. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}